## Summary (paraphrased)

The post shares a 4-step AI SEO framework that led one client to 2,300% AI traffic growth and appearance in 90+ AI overviews (vs zero before).

### 1. Finding AI Opportunities
- Use Surfer AI Tracker / Ahrefs Brand Radar to see how often AI platforms mention your brand vs competitors.
- Filter for AI keywords competitors are winning that you’re not.
- Those are the exact topics you need to target.

### 2. Content Strategy
- Write directly and skip the fluff (AI hates filler content).
- Use conversational tone (how people actually speak, not keyword stuffing).
- Structure with clear H1/H2/H3 hierarchy.
- Add TLDR summaries at the top of articles.

### 3. Building Trust Signals
- Claim and optimize Google Business, Yelp, LinkedIn profiles.
- Get high-quality backlinks from relevant domains.
- Include expert quotes and author bios with credentials.
- Showcase certifications and awards prominently.
- Add case studies with real data.

### 4. (Implied) Monitoring & Iteration
- Track AI traffic and AI overviews.
- Iterate on content and trust signals.

## Why this post is high-signal

- Based on 6 months of testing AI SEO tactics for real clients. 
- Includes concrete results: 2,300% growth, 90+ AI overviews.  
- Provides a repeatable 4-step framework, not just theory. 
